                "title": "Handout: Newton's Laws Flowchart",
                "text": "Start: Object in Motion?\n  ↓\nIs Net Force Zero?\n  ├── YES → Velocity Constant (1st Law)\n  └── NO  → Accelerates F=ma (2nd Law)\n\nForce Interaction?\n  └── Always comes in PAIRS (3rd Law)"
