                "sectionId": "math-t001-s002",
                "type": "text",
                "title": "Handout: Exponent Rules Map",
                "text": "Operation -> Rule\nMultiply Same Base -> ADD Exponents (x^a * x^b = x^(a+b))\nDivide Same Base -> SUBTRACT Exponents (x^a / x^b = x^(a-b))\nPower to Power -> MULTIPLY Exponents ((x^a)^b = x^ab)"
            },
            {
                "sectionId": "math-t001-s003",
                "type": "formula",
                "title": "General Compounding",
                "text": "A = P(1 + r/n)^(nt)\nWhere:\nA = Future Value, P = Principal\nr = rate, n = times compounded"
            }
        ],
